{"tid":1977195,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛指控港台重錄提問、剪輯片段以扭曲訪問內容，港台堅決否認","createTime":"2020-04-17T19:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T10:59:48.000Z","uid":310817,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"640afd0fe8b76ef1ecbad957c67a05a8a73973fe","tid":1977195,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:04:05.000Z","msg":"引述自端傳媒<br />\n<br />\n香港電台英文節目《The Pulse》上月通過視像訪問世界衛生組織助理總幹事艾禾特（Bruce Aylward），期間艾禾特多次迴避有關台灣問題，引發兩岸以至國際輿論爭議。世衛發言人回覆傳媒查詢，指控港台曾經剪輯訪問片段、補錄記者提問，令訪問「內容扭曲、陳述失實」，而港台堅決否認指控。<br />\n\r<br />\n美國《華盛頓郵報》記者 Emily Rauhala 在 Twitter 公開世衛發言人回應。世衛發言人指出，港台記者當日不斷提問有關台灣的抗疫表現，而艾禾特已經多次解釋，有關專家未曾到訪的地區，他無法作出揣測及評價；然而，港台事後重新拍攝記者提問、並剪輯訪問片段，以創造扭曲內容和失實陳述。<br />\n\r<br />\n世衛發言人舉例聲稱，當日訪問連線中斷後，艾禾特主動要求重新連線，但節目內容顯示是記者重新致電艾禾達。世衛發言人又指，港台事後拒絕提供未經剪輯的訪問片段。<br />\n\r<br />\n港台機構傳訊組總監伍曼儀接受香港英語獨立網媒 HKFP 查詢，堅決否認世衛的指控。伍曼儀強調，當日完成採訪後，並無重新拍攝記者提問的片段，而連線中斷後、也是港台主動重新接通視像會議。<br />\n<br />\n文章鏈接：<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200417-evening-brief/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200417-evening-brief%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=36ff00ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200417-evening-brief/</a><br />\n相關鏈接：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/emilyrauhala/status/1250504156303052801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Femilyrauhala%2Fstatus%2F1250504156303052801&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=f6b554e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Femilyrauhala%2Fstatus%2F1250504156303052801&h=541e9053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/emilyrauhala/status/1250504156303052801</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hongkongfp.com/2020/04/16/hong-kong-broadcaster-rejects-who-claim-that-interview-with-top-doctor-was-distorted/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkongfp.com%2F2020%2F04%2F16%2Fhong-kong-broadcaster-rejects-who-claim-that-interview-with-top-doctor-was-distorted%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=89ce579f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hongkongfp.com/2020/04/16/hong-kong-broadcaster-rejects-who-claim-that-interview-with-top-doctor-was-distorted/</a><br />\n<br />\n見冇咩中文媒體報道，所以分享上嚟，唔知有咩做到，但大家盡量推港台twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thepulse_rthk/status/1251027368195452928?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthepulse_rthk%2Fstatus%2F1251027368195452928%3Fs%3D19&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=c246f7c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthepulse_rthk%2Fstatus%2F1251027368195452928%3Fs%3D19&h=dfbda960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thepulse_rthk/status/1251027368195452928?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"608108bd54dfd43ec4d98f36bc420b70872881a9","tid":1977195,"uid":258578,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:05:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9eee096b0c611cd6dcc4ec8f364edaa9d7615275","tid":1977195,"uid":140538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:09:06.000Z","msg":"推tweet 啦啦屌"},{"pid":"a0ea55c3e0c6229b88426a598ebce413497291f6","tid":1977195,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:16:10.000Z","msg":"立場: 拒回應台灣成員資格 世衛發言人指控港台 曾剪輯片段致歪曲、失實陳述 港台否認指控<br />\n<br />\n香港電台英文節目 The Pulse 上月視象電話訪問世衛助理總幹事艾華特（Bruce Aylward），期間詢問世衛會否重新考慮接納台灣加入，但艾華特拒絕回答。據《華盛頓郵報》記者 Emily Rauhala 指，世衛發言人回覆查詢時，指港台曾經剪輯過訪問片段，令「內容扭曲、陳述失實」（substantial distortion and misrepresentation），又指當時視像會議斷線後，是艾華特主動回電港台記者。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》記者 Emily Rauhala 在 twitter 公開世衛的回覆，之後 HKFP 亦向世衛查詢並獲回覆，發言人指在當時訪問中，艾華特多次重申他不會回答職權以外的事，但港台「重新拍攝（reshot）」訪問過程及記者發問問題的畫面，剪輯後令訪問內容扭曲，港台亦拒絕向世衛提供未經剪輯的訪問片段。<br />\n<br />\nHKFP 引述港台機構傳訊組總監伍曼儀回應，指堅決否認「歪曲和虛假陳述」的指控。她指，在完成採訪後，港台並沒有對受訪者或記者發問問題重新拍攝，當時亦是港台主動重新接通視像會議。<br />\n<br />\n港台記者三問台灣問題 助理總幹事全避答<br />\n<br />\n有關節目是在 3 月 28 日播出的 The Pulse，邀請到當時仍為世衛助理總幹事的艾華特接受訪問。艾華特為世衛在武漢肺炎疫情中的角色辯護，認為世衛已向世界各地發出足夠訊息。節目其後提及台灣在防疫中表現較其他東亞地區為佳，而且早在去年 12 月底已向世衛發生病毒可能人傳人的警告，而歐盟早前在視像會議上有邀請台灣給予意見。<br />\n<br />\nThe Pulse 的記者唐若韞先是問艾華特，世衛是否重新考慮台灣的會籍問題，艾華特先是沉默約 10 秒，其後指自己聽不到提問。唐若韞其後指自己會重覆問題，艾華特指毋需要，建議另轉話題，但唐堅持問台灣會籍問題，視像通話就此中斷；唐其後再致電艾華特，第三度詢問世衛對台灣加入的睇法，艾華特指中國在抗疫表現中很好，並要求結束對話。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華早前表示，港台在該節目當中的表達，有違一個中國的原則及《香港電台約章》，稱廣播處長梁家榮必須對此負責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8B%92%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC-%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E6%9B%BE%E5%89%AA%E8%BC%AF%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%AA%E6%9B%B2-%E5%A4%B1%E5%AF%A6%E9%99%B3%E8%BF%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2589%25AA%25E8%25BC%25AF%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25AA%25E6%259B%25B2-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%25BF%25B0-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=a4147781\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25A0%25BC-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2589%25AA%25E8%25BC%25AF%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25AA%25E6%259B%25B2-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%25BF%25B0-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&h=1c3d5221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8B%92%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC-%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0-%E6%9B%BE%E5%89%AA%E8%BC%AF%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%AA%E6%9B%B2-%E5%A4%B1%E5%AF%A6%E9%99%B3%E8%BF%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"e9832b1a451477ba78a2d88ba6afe38fff17f5ad","tid":1977195,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:17:00.000Z","msg":"蘋果: WHO稱訪問曾剪輯 港台：一刀未剪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港台英文電視節目《The Pulse》早前以視像方式，訪問世衞助理總幹事艾爾沃德時談及台灣事件，被商經局局長邱騰華以「莫須有」罪名，憑空指摘節目有違一個中國原則及《香港電台約章》，事件續有餘波，《華盛頓郵報》昨引述世衞回覆查詢，反指控港台訪問片段曾作剪輯，造成嚴重扭曲及失實陳述，而港台事後拒向世衞提供未剪輯片段。港台發言人回覆英文網媒《HKFP》就堅決否認指控，強調涉事過程均是來自18秒未曾剪裁的鏡頭片段，亦因為有關片段引來國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n拒提供片段 保編採獨立<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》記者向世衞就事件再查詢，想了解世衞是否有澄清時，獲回覆指在訪問中，港台採訪者曾重複向艾爾沃德就台灣應對新冠狀病毒情況發問，惟艾爾沃德以團隊未曾到訪有關地區為由拒作推測，繼而指控港台之後重拍採訪者提問及對訪問作剪輯，從成造成嚴重扭曲及失實陳述。<br />\n<br />\n世衞又指，艾爾沃德在視像通話訪問斷線後，其實是他即時重新來電，而港台拒向世衞提供未剪輯片段版本。<br />\n<br />\n不過，港台機構傳訊及節目標準組總監伍曼儀回覆《HKFP》查詢時，堅決否認有關指控。伍曼儀指，在該採訪後，沒有對採訪者及其發問進行重新拍攝，同時強調訪問中，受訪者表示無法聽到重複問題，提出轉到另一問題，然後表示不能聽到及出現斷線，均在同一18秒內未剪輯鏡頭下發生，而正是這一片段，引起了國際關注。她又解釋，拒向世衞提供片段的決定，與世界各地新聞媒體一般做法相同，以確保編採獨立性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200417/M5RX7HJNI4H3B5CP3TWGXNGBQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2FM5RX7HJNI4H3B5CP3TWGXNGBQU%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=72556849\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2FM5RX7HJNI4H3B5CP3TWGXNGBQU%2F&h=a30b10e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200417/M5RX7HJNI4H3B5CP3TWGXNGBQU/</a>"},{"pid":"28cfaaaad1f5c5cfceeab1ac6f6ed471634ec220","tid":1977195,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:20:31.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a25f5b0ca23b5937378a625dcf4e252f2b05b9","tid":1977195,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28cfaaaad1f5c5cfceeab1ac6f6ed471634ec220","tid":1977195,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:20:31.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0928b0493f5b36f87bde8569b274666e0f634e88","tid":1977195,"uid":116146,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:22:49.000Z","msg":"再反駁只會令到個畫面更肉酸"},{"pid":"0917ecf9ea315fde30f771b5a8bba78c3115b4da","tid":1977195,"uid":321837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:23:12.000Z","msg":"WHO似係謊言部"},{"pid":"3df15c7cb803f73285df4f505e83e7fbd7758b28","tid":1977195,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T19:23:24.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"22a98eb2561f1d334cafc090058fc209053df668","tid":1977195,"uid":186039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-1